milestones.description: Paras Khadka and Khakurel's 13-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Malla and Airee
Paras Khadka and Rohit Paudel's 16-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between Sompal Kami and Airee
Paras Khadka and Aarif Sheikh's 47-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 10 between Basant Regmi and Airee
Sompal Kami and Aarif Sheikh's 23-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 18 between Gauchan and Airee
Sompal Kami and Lamichhane's 41-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Gauchan and Lamichhane
Bhandari and Lamichhane's 12-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Gauchan and Vesawkar
Bhandari has conceded the most runs in an innings (43) in ODIs for NEP, going past Lamichhane's record of 42
This is the highest match aggregate (431) involving teams Netherlands & Nepal in ODIs
Sompal Kami has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (38) in an innings in ODIs for NEP, going past Malla's 32
Sompal Kami has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (3) in ODIs for NEP, going past Airee's 1
Sompal Kami's 61 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for NEP), surpassing Malla's 51
Aarif Sheikh has broken the record for most ducks (1) in ODIs for NEP, going past Karan KC's 1
Aarif Sheikh has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for NEP, going past Airee
